        <scopecontent id="aspace_948c91914b19acf351f29fc4ffc5a142">
          <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
          <p>This series contains records of appropriations for the Humanities Division compiled from the Minutes of the Foundation from 1929 until 1949, Humanities Program reviews and fellowship surveys undertaken between 1934 and 1949, and occasional reports. Also contained in this series are reports generated from other divisions of the Foundation or treating the Humanities Division as part of the Foundation's general program. A small number of pamphlets collected by Stevens dealing with Foundation grantees concludes this series. Most of the material in this series is duplicated in the archives of The Rockefeller Foundation.</p>
        </scopecontent>
